Auto-Forward Smart Speed — Attribution and Free Access Licence
Version 1.0

Copyright:
© John2022FR. AFSS-specific changes, configuration, naming, assets, packaging and release are by John2022FR.

Technical base:
Auto-Forward Smart Speed is a fork / adaptation based on QuickStep by GayCookie.
QuickStep was released under the WTFPL.

Permissions:
You may use this mod on DayZ servers.
You may use this mod on monetized DayZ servers, provided that the mod itself remains freely accessible to players.
You may modify this mod for your own use or for server-specific needs.
You may repack or redistribute this mod, provided that all attribution and free-access conditions are respected.
You may publish modified versions, provided that they are clearly identified as modified versions and do not claim to be the original work.

Attribution requirements:
Any redistribution, repack, modified version, server pack or derivative work must clearly credit:
- John2022FR for Auto-Forward Smart Speed;
- GayCookie for QuickStep, the original technical base.

The credits must not be removed, hidden, obscured or replaced in a way that suggests another person is the original author of Auto-Forward Smart Speed or QuickStep.

Free access requirement:
The mod itself must remain freely accessible.

You may not sell, rent, license, paywall, or otherwise charge money specifically for access to this mod.
You may not sell this mod as part of a paid modpack without written permission from John2022FR.
You may not make access to this mod itself conditional on payment.

Monetized servers:
Monetized DayZ servers may use this mod.
Donations, subscriptions, VIP systems, priority queue payments, cosmetic payments and other server monetization systems are allowed, provided that they do not sell access to this mod itself.

If you want to include this mod in a paid product, paid modpack, commercial package, or any system where access to the mod itself is monetized, you must obtain written permission from John2022FR. Such permission may require a royalty agreement.

No false authorship:
You may not claim authorship of the original work.
You may not slightly modify the code and present the resulting mod as an original work.
You may not remove the history of the fork, the credit to John2022FR, or the credit to GayCookie / QuickStep.

No warranty:
This mod is provided as-is, without warranty of any kind. Use it at your own risk.

